title CI/CD - EventFlow Taller

actor Developer

Developer -> GitHub : Push a main

GitHub -> "GitHub Actions" : Dispara workflow CI

rectangle "Pipeline CI" {
    "Checkout" --> "Build Simulado"
    "Build Simulado" --> "Tests Simulados"
    "Tests Simulados" --> "Copiar index.html a /build"
}

"Copiar index.html a /build" --> GitHub : Publica artefactos (simulado)

@enduml
